elements.name: Como usuario, quiero crear un post, y si no me gusta eliminarlo.

steps.name: I enter post title "Nueva publicacin eliminar" in the content field
I enter post content "contenido de la nueva publicacin eliminar" in the content field
I click publish post, right now
I verify that a post with text "Nueva publicacin eliminar" exists
I click on a post with name "Nueva publicacin eliminar"
I click on the post options element
I scroll to the delete post button and click it
I verify that a confirmation modal exists
I verify that a post with text "Nueva publicacin eliminar" does not exist
